data.title: The Dominion of Canada with Newfoundland and an Excursion to Alaska: Handbook for Travellers by Baedecker, Karl: Very Good (1907) Third edition.
data.meta_description: Third edition. - Karl Baedeker, Leipzig, Germany - 1907 - Condition: Very Good - 16mo (6"x4"). 331pp. Red flex covers, blindstamped with giltstamped titles. Marbled textblock edges. 13 full color maps, 5 of which are fold-outs and "12 plans". Light shelfwear: rubbed edges, warp, soiling. Pages toned. Heavily foxed endpapers. Slight warp throughout. Lower half of first fold-out loose at gutter. - The Dominion of Canada with Newfoundland and an Excursion to Alaska: Handbook for Travellers
